            <thetext>Currently nightly line of Webkit and this way also Safari 4 will support getBoundingClientRect for high performance location detection for DOM elements. Currently qooxdoo&#39;s code uses this method in IE and Firefox since version 3. The code path should also be implemented for recent Webkits for performance reasons.

See also:
http://sideshowbarker.net/2009/02/12/getboundingclientrect/</thetext>
